	<title>Standard ports</title>

	<para>
		The protocols Eclipse NeoSCADA provides are normally based on plain
		TCP
		client/server protocols. Each driver and application provides
		services
		on different TCP ports. The follow map provides a list of
		<quote>well known ports</quote>
		in the Eclipse NeoSCADA system.
	</para>

	<para>
		For an update to list, see also the Eclipse NeoSCADA Wiki page at
		<link
			xlink:href="https://wiki.eclipse.org/EclipseSCADA/Documentation/StandardPorts">https://wiki.eclipse.org/EclipseSCADA/Documentation/StandardPorts
		</link>
		.
	</para>

